  "title": "Two brazilian ships in the Atlantic Ocean reported a large UFO sighting [1986]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/13/two-brazilian-ships-in-the-atlantic-ocean-reported-a-large-ufo-sighting-1986/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1Nc",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>August 18, 1986</strong>. &#8211; Occurrence transcript released in the Chief Controller&#8217;s Assistant book &#8211; &#8220;At 19:14, the ACC-BS [Area Control Center of Brasília-DF] received information that two ships that were in the coordinates 1830S/03850W reported to EMBRATEL&#8217;s coastal station that they saw a large unidentified flying object heading towards the Northwest. &#8220;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.247. “Transcrição de ocorrências de avistamento de objetos voadores não identificados em diversas regiões e localidades, por embarcações e aeronaves no decorrer de agosto de 1986</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>August 18, 1986. &#8211; Occurrence transcript released in the Chief Controller&#8217;s Assistant book &#8211; &#8220;At 19:14, the ACC-BS [Area Control Center of Brasília-DF] received information that two ships that were in the coordinates 1830S/03850W reported to EMBRATEL&#8217;s coastal station that they saw a large unidentified flying object heading towards the Northwest. &#8220; Cf. ARQUIVO NACIONAL [&hellip;]</p>\n",
